{"tid":345904,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[月經] 小畫家 地點","createTime":"2017-08-03T13:04:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T18:18:46.000Z","uid":78083,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2a4de8ae7f6e7ea96c8314f7718c97869a37eec9","tid":345904,"uid":78083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T13:04:38.000Z","msg":"Yoyo，大家好，我係島佬，冇錢讀藝術，日日讀屎片<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n為咗紀念聽講要收皮嘅小畫家，所以開返嚟玩吓<br />\n<br />\n1) 地點，景點，地方，真實定幻想你點話點好啦<br />\n<br />\n2) Size一般係1600X900px<br />\n（做桌面應該啱啩，其他就要另外講）<br />\n<br />\n3) 可以加字，但係字醜<br />\n<br />\n畀面就正皮啦，多謝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/I1xDXBy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FI1xDXBy.png&h=76d68ece&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解要係地點？<br />\n因為&hellip;&hellip;我係樓主？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c0fabd1cd69be89670627090ef507470f90cc61","tid":345904,"uid":106927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T13:08:08.000Z","msg":"唔知你畫乜但正咗先"},{"pid":"c9f58df8a6531922c7c262d96735ded6e82e03a1","tid":345904,"uid":91560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T13:08:17.000Z","msg":"alice in wonderland個樹林景 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a517bbaee99475a76cf8840d5873929dd5f80f1e","tid":345904,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T13:09:41.000Z","msg":"Saber既 Avalon"},{"pid":"891f5a3123013c5ef28ca7a7c88e2c1014cc1ef5","tid":345904,"uid":51981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T13:11:55.000Z","msg":"薰衣草田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a500ab641234c20596eacb9dbdccaf1413774ae7","tid":345904,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":